#: includes/admin/class-product-migrator.php:140
msgid "The Migration Wizard simplifies the process of reorganizing your knowledge base by converting your existing sections into products and mapping articles to their corresponding products. This ensures a more structured, user-friendly, and discoverable knowledge base. Below is a step-by-step overview of what the wizard will do. No changes will be applied until you confirm and initiate the migration."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-product-migrator.php:142
msgid "Convert Sections to Products: Each top-level section in your knowledge base will be transformed into a distinct product, preserving its identity and purpose."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-product-migrator.php:143
msgid "Map Articles to Products: Articles will be intelligently assigned to their respective products based on the existing section hierarchy, ensuring no content is lost or misplaced."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-product-migrator.php:144
msgid "Handle Sub-Sections: Any sub-sections (descendant sections) will be processed to correctly associate their articles with the appropriate product, maintaining organizational clarity."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-product-migrator.php:145
msgid "Remove Old Sections: Once articles are mapped, the original top-level sections will be removed to streamline your knowledge base structure."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-product-migrator.php:146
msgid "Preview with Dry Run: Use the dry-run option to simulate the migration process without making any changes, allowing you to review the outcome before committing."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-product-migrator.php:147
msgid "Confirm and Migrate: After reviewing the dry run, you can start the migration with confidence, knowing your knowledge base will be restructured for improved organization and accessibility."
msgstr ""

